<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 10:07:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>人质交易和拉法攻势达到临界点，以色列可能会崩溃</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/hostage-deal-and-rafah-op-reach-tipping-point-and-israel-could-fall-either-way/0000018f-3a0e-d0b5-a59f-3bcf9a540000</link><description>人质交易陷入了内塔尼亚胡的“岩石”和辛瓦尔的“困境”之间，全世界都在等待哈马斯对当前提议的答复。彻底的胜利”被认为是</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 03:00:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/hostage-deal-and-rafah-op-reach-tipping-point-and-israel-could-fall-either-way/0000018f-3a0e-d0b5-a59f-3bcf9a540000</guid></item><item><title>尽管一再要求，以色列总理办公室仍未提交向哈马斯转移资金的文件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-pms-office-yet-to-submit-files-on-transfer-of-funds-to-hamas-despite-requests/0000018f-3a5f-d8fb-a1df-bf7f5b780000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的局没有遵守国家审计长要求的在 10 月 7 日之前对政府和军队进行调查的文件。总理办公室称这一声明是“战争时期不必要的冲突”，并表示他们已配合所有要求</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 03:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-pms-office-yet-to-submit-files-on-transfer-of-funds-to-hamas-despite-requests/0000018f-3a5f-d8fb-a1df-bf7f5b780000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡是不断送给哈马斯及其种族主义联盟伙伴的礼物</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-the-gift-that-keeps-on-giving-to-hamas-and-his-racist-coalition-partners/0000018f-3afb-d414-a5bf-bbff91c40000</link><description>以色列总理的策略很明确：安抚支持其政府的战争贩子，并向哈马斯暗示它不应同意任何协议 ■ 内塔尼亚胡实际上可以从被国际刑事法院宣布为战犯中受益</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 03:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-the-gift-that-keeps-on-giving-to-hamas-and-his-racist-coalition-partners/0000018f-3afb-d414-a5bf-bbff91c40000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其确认停止与以色列贸易，直至加沙永久停火、援助自由流动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article-live/eight-syrian-soldiers-injured-in-alleged-israeli-strike/0000018f-3c41-d516-afbf-fec39bd90000</link><description>国际刑事法院检察官办公室谴责干涉其工作的公正性和独立性，因为对以色列官员的逮捕令正在接受审查。以色列/沙特就巴勒斯坦国协议建立关系 ■ 半岛电视台禁令投票推迟至周日 ■ 伊朗称已释放四月份扣押的与以色列有关的船只上的船员</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 02:29:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article-live/eight-syrian-soldiers-injured-in-alleged-israeli-strike/0000018f-3c41-d516-afbf-fec39bd90000</guid></item><item><title>基布兹称，德罗尔·奥尔 (Dror Or) 于 10 月 7 日被杀，据信是加沙的以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/dror-or-believed-to-be-among-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-was-killed-on-oct-7-kibbutz-says/0000018f-3bf9-d8f8-abbf-7bf9ff9d0000</link><description>奥尔的妻子被谋杀，他的孩子被扣为人质；他的尸体仍被哈马斯扣押</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 01:10:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/dror-or-believed-to-be-among-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-was-killed-on-oct-7-kibbutz-says/0000018f-3bf9-d8f8-abbf-7bf9ff9d0000</guid></item><item><title>“在玻利维亚做犹太人并不容易。我需要在这里，在以色列”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-05-03/ty-article/.highlight/its-not-easy-being-a-jew-in-bolivia-i-need-to-be-here-in-israel/0000018f-3af7-d414-a5bf-bbf798a80000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名犹太裔玻利维亚人思考自 70 年代居住在这里以来以色列发生的变化，一名俄罗斯移民解释了他离开圣彼得堡前往特拉维夫的原因</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 21:16:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-05-03/ty-article/.highlight/its-not-easy-being-a-jew-in-bolivia-i-need-to-be-here-in-israel/0000018f-3af7-d414-a5bf-bbf798a80000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯外交官称埃及试图说服哈马斯在达成协议后不要重启战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/arab-diplomats-say-egypt-trying-to-convince-hamas-not-to-restart-war-after-deal/0000018f-3ae6-d17f-adcf-fbe75dee0000</link><description>外交官们证实了黎巴嫩的一份报告，称埃及的提议不包括以色列不返回加沙地带的详细承诺，埃及正试图说服哈马斯，该提议将保证该激进组织的安全</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 20:45:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/arab-diplomats-say-egypt-trying-to-convince-hamas-not-to-restart-war-after-deal/0000018f-3ae6-d17f-adcf-fbe75dee0000</guid></item><item><title>被任命的以色列警察局长与一名被定罪的诈骗犯之间的密谋对话</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/the-conspiring-conversation-between-the-appointed-police-chief-and-a-convicted-fraudster/0000018f-3a7b-d516-afbf-fefb5ade0000</link><description>2015 年，本·格维尔 (Ben Gvir) 挑选的警察局长阿夫沙洛姆·佩莱德 (Avshalom Peled) 在电话中请求他的朋友摩西·达顿 (Moshe Dadon) 帮助掩盖他家中的建筑违规行为。他不知道的是，国家反欺诈部门正在监听这个电话，调查达东。通话记录已经公布</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 20:23:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/the-conspiring-conversation-between-the-appointed-police-chief-and-a-convicted-fraudster/0000018f-3a7b-d516-afbf-fefb5ade0000</guid></item><item><title>卢旺达种族灭绝？布隆迪大屠杀？以色列一切如常</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/genocide-in-rwanda-massacre-in-burundi-its-business-as-usual-for-israel/0000018f-3ad3-d414-a5bf-bbf752870000</link><description>胡图族在卢旺达屠杀数十万图西族的二十年前，图西族在布隆迪屠杀了胡图族。有关以色列向卢旺达提供军事援助的记录仍然是绝密，但解密的外交部有关布隆迪的信件暗示对种族屠杀漠不关心</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 20:18:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/genocide-in-rwanda-massacre-in-burundi-its-business-as-usual-for-israel/0000018f-3ad3-d414-a5bf-bbf752870000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫描绘了加沙儿童的痛苦</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-paints-the-pain-of-gazan-children/0000018f-39b7-d516-afbf-fff725ce0000</link><description>《纯真被破坏：战时的儿童》拒绝对加沙的死亡和破坏视而不见，以色列纪录片周 DocAviv 和耶路撒冷作家节将于本月晚些时候回归</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 20:06:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-paints-the-pain-of-gazan-children/0000018f-39b7-d516-afbf-fff725ce0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对加沙拉法的入侵将是致命的。有一个更好的办法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-02/ty-article/.highlight/an-israeli-invasion-of-gazas-rafah-will-be-deadly-there-is-a-better-way/0000018f-3a04-d9c3-abcf-7a75d7af0000</link><description>拆除拉法隧道是以色列-加沙边境长期安全的关键要求。但在做出攻击加沙南部城市的重大决定之前，以色列必须仔细研究这一替代方案</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 19:57:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-02/ty-article/.highlight/an-israeli-invasion-of-gazas-rafah-will-be-deadly-there-is-a-better-way/0000018f-3a04-d9c3-abcf-7a75d7af0000</guid></item><item><title>解救人质的内塔尼亚胡兄弟的私人信件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-private-letters-of-the-netanyahu-brother-who-did-rescue-hostages/0000018f-3a62-d9c3-abcf-7a77a6f00000</link><description>重读 1976 年在恩德培英勇牺牲的约尼·内塔尼亚胡 (Yoni Netanyahu) 的信件，可能会揭示他弟弟本杰明 (Benjamin) 令人不安的性格。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 19:39:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-private-letters-of-the-netanyahu-brother-who-did-rescue-hostages/0000018f-3a62-d9c3-abcf-7a77a6f00000</guid></item><item><title>自战争开始以来，西岸整个地区的社区已被清空</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/since-the-war-began-entire-areas-of-the-west-bank-have-been-emptied-of-their-communities/0000018f-39a9-d9c3-abcf-7bfd66980000</link><description>10 月 7 日，约旦河西岸的定居者暴力达到了顶峰：自此，18 个巴勒斯坦牧民社区被迫背井离乡，居民现在住在其他村庄郊区的临时住所里，一贫如洗，对未来感到焦虑</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 19:33:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/since-the-war-began-entire-areas-of-the-west-bank-have-been-emptied-of-their-communities/0000018f-39a9-d9c3-abcf-7bfd66980000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，土耳其在加沙战争期间停止了与以色列的所有贸易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/turkey-reportedly-halts-all-trade-with-israel-amid-war-in-gaza/0000018f-3a77-d9c3-abcf-7a770e3a0000</link><description>土耳其尚未正式宣布此举，正值加沙战争期间两国关系紧张，但以色列进口商已经抱怨发货延迟</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 18:38:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/turkey-reportedly-halts-all-trade-with-israel-amid-war-in-gaza/0000018f-3a77-d9c3-abcf-7a770e3a0000</guid></item><item><title>反以色列校园活动人士不是纳粹分子。但他们是特朗普法西斯主义的同谋</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/anti-israel-campus-activists-arent-nazis-but-theyre-complicit-with-trumps-fascism/0000018f-39c6-d8fb-a1df-bde68ff70000</link><description>当内塔尼亚胡可笑地将亲巴勒斯坦学生与纳粹进行比较时，他只是让极少数享有特权的少数人更容易坚持认为他们不是真正的反犹太主义者，而只是“反犹太复国主义者”</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 18:03:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/anti-israel-campus-activists-arent-nazis-but-theyre-complicit-with-trumps-fascism/0000018f-39c6-d8fb-a1df-bde68ff70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 209 天：据报道土耳其停止与以色列的所有贸易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-209-turkey-reportedly-halts-all-trade-with-israel/0000018f-3a31-d516-afbf-fef3536e0001</link><description>哈马斯代表团将在开罗继续停战谈判 ■ 当被问及以色列总理内塔尼亚胡承诺以色列无论是否达成释放人质协议都将进入拉法时，布林肯说让我们关注他们在做什么吧 ■ 据报道，土耳其已停止与以色列的所有进出口贸易 ■ 以色列国家安全委员会向马尔默发出新的旅行警告 ■ 战争爆发 209 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 16:52:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-209-turkey-reportedly-halts-all-trade-with-israel/0000018f-3a31-d516-afbf-fef3536e0001</guid></item><item><title>以色列三大食品制造商宣布乳制品涨价</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/three-major-israeli-food-manufacturers-announce-price-hikes-on-dairy-products/0000018f-39ad-d516-afbf-ffef561f0000</link><description>食品巨头 Tnuva、Strauss 和 Tara 宣布，他们将提高酸奶和奶酪等非管制乳制品以及冷冻蔬菜和家禽等其他主食的价格。这些公司将价格上涨归咎于战争对原材料供应的影响</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 14:52:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/three-major-israeli-food-manufacturers-announce-price-hikes-on-dairy-products/0000018f-39ad-d516-afbf-ffef561f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警察因袭击反司法政变抗议者而被起诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-officer-indicted-for-assaulting-anti-judicial-coup-protester/0000018f-3970-d0b5-a59f-39f551250000</link><description>起诉书称，在 2023 年的一次抗议活动中，骑警多次袭击骑马的抗议者 Yael Reuveni。这是针对警察在反司法政变抗议期间使用武力的首份起诉书</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 14:17:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-officer-indicted-for-assaulting-anti-judicial-coup-protester/0000018f-3970-d0b5-a59f-39f551250000</guid></item><item><title>极端正统派领导人必须举行成人礼——并为人质获释而奋斗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/ultra-orthodox-leaders-must-do-a-mitzvah-and-fight-for-the-hostages-release/0000018f-3968-d8fb-a1df-bd6e4c750000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 13:59:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/ultra-orthodox-leaders-must-do-a-mitzvah-and-fight-for-the-hostages-release/0000018f-3968-d8fb-a1df-bd6e4c750000</guid></item><item><title>死者家属要求以色列部长和议员不要在阵亡将士纪念日仪式上发言</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/bereaved-families-ask-israeli-ministers-mks-not-to-speak-in-memorial-day-ceremonies/0000018f-38f9-d9c3-abcf-7afd943f0000</link><description>以色列议会公布了阵亡将士纪念日仪式的出席名单。极右翼财政部长贝扎莱尔·斯莫特里奇 (Bezalel Smotrich) 将于卡法萨巴公墓露面，该公墓埋葬着 10 月 7 日阵亡的以色列士兵罗尼·埃谢尔 (Roni Eshel)。她的父亲说：“我觉得他们似乎是故意伤害我们更多”</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 13:31:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-02/ty-article/.premium/bereaved-families-ask-israeli-ministers-mks-not-to-speak-in-memorial-day-ceremonies/0000018f-38f9-d9c3-abcf-7afd943f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>